Geological feature inventory: Streamlined landform (Crag and tail /drumlin / flute / groove)
Marine bar form (Contourite drift/ sediment apron/ sediment drift/ sediment lobe/energetic wave or current regime)
Submarine canyon (canyon/ canyon head / canyon mouth / tributary canyon)
Buried or exposed eustatic escarpment (excessive seabed gradient)
Depositional zone (aka. Accumulation zone; compressional domain) can include all mass movement (topple/fall/debris flows etc)
Evacuation zone (aka. Headwall domain; depletion zone; extensional domain) can include all mass movement (topple/fall/debris flows etc)
Clay Tectonics (polygonal fracture networks and folded layers/diapirs)
